Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <for-loop> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT for-loop (loop-var+,connection*)>
 <!ATTLIST for-loop
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;"
      trailing-comment    CDATA     "&#10;" >
